| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3722 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 87dcdd44-22b1-5f47-af1b-b5de62ec2659"
